summary: This mod is a racemenu preset that includes the likeness of a woman named Michelle Tate, who was on the SyFy channel paranormal-themed reality shows ghost hunters and ghost hunters academy for some time.
descriptionHtml:
[b]This mod is a racemenu preset that includes the likeness of a woman named Michelle Tate, who was on the SyFy channelparanormal-themed reality shows ghost hunters and ghost hunters academy for some time.[/b]
 
[color=#00ff00]===INSTALLATION===
[b]Step 1. After downloading this file, go into the directory [i]my computer/local disk/program files x86/steam/steamapps/common/skyrim/data/skse/plugins/chargen/presets[/i] and copy and paste the file Michelle Tate.jslot into there.[/b]
 
[b]Step 2. Boot the game up, go into racemenu by typing "showracemenu" in the console, then click "presets" on the bar in the top right of the screen, and press F9 to load presets and load "Susan Slaughter Preset.jslot" (it should be in there) and voila, there you are![/b][/color]
 
[color=#ff0000]===REQUIREMENTS===
*SKSE 1.7.2 or above
*Racemenu (latest version)
*SG Eyebrows
*True Eyes
*Dimonized UNP Skinny body
*SG Hair Pack 268 Edition (google this mod to find it's download location, it is not anywhere on nexus or loverslab)
 
Make 100% sure that you have the above mods installed before playing this or else this will not work properly![/color]
 
[color=#00ffff][b]===Optional/Recommended===
Sexy Vanilla Female Armor for UNP and SevenBase with BBP
Bracelets By Ezuka
Sexy Swimsuit and bikinis for CBBE
Wedding Rings By Ezuka
FNIS Sexy Walk/FNIS 5.2[/b][/color]
